<div class="articleBody">
        
    
                                                                                <p>
                    ABIDJAN, Ivory Coast &mdash; The uniformed men came in the morning, while the youths in the opposition neighborhood were sleeping. Some wore masks.        </p>
                                                </div>
<div class="articleInline runaroundLeft">
    		

							<div class="inlineImage module">
	<div class="image">
		         <div class="icon enlargeThis"><a href="javascript:pop_me_up2('http://www.nytimes.com/imagepages/2010/12/11/11ivory-web1.html','11ivory_web1_html','width=720,height=562,scrollbars=yes,toolbars=no,resizable=yes')">Enlarge This Image</a></div>
